descriptionHtml:
Apna thikaana is an online platform developed to simplify the life of the student. It provides a platform for the student as well as for professional to search for the dream hostel or PG rooms at just the tip of fingertip.

Apna thikaana is started to ease the life of the student as well as of professional so they can focus on study and work. We have tied up with the landlord owner, hotel, and hostel owners to provide the best facilities.
We are one of the leading hostel service providers in Patna. Our budget-friendly deal, tie-up with some of the best hostel provider, as well as easy convenience of booking, and most importantly our dedication towards the improvising the life of a student by providing easy hostel & PG services at just tip of the fingertip.
